{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":570,"text":"Photography has been my passion"},{"time":2056,"text":"ever since I was old enough to pick up a camera,"},{"time":4834,"text":"but today I want to share with you"},{"time":7194,"text":"the 15 most treasured photos of mine,"},{"time":10476,"text":"and I didn't take any of them."},{"time":12071,"text":"There were no art directors, no stylists,"},{"time":14962,"text":"no chance for reshoots, not even any regard for lighting."},{"time":19398,"text":"In fact, most of them were taken by random tourists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23674,"text":"My story begins"},{"time":25186,"text":"when I was in New York City for a speaking engagement,"},{"time":27704,"text":"and my wife took this picture of me holding my daughter"},{"time":30467,"text":"on her first birthday. We're on the corner of 57th and 5th."},{"time":34903,"text":"We happened to be back in New York exactly a year later,"},{"time":38444,"text":"so we decided to take the same picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41843,"text":"Well you can see where this is going."},{"time":44092,"text":"Approaching my daughter's third birthday,"},{"time":45826,"text":"my wife said, \"Hey, why don't you take Sabina back to New York"},{"time":48268,"text":"and make it a father-daughter trip, and continue the ritual?\""},{"time":52399,"text":"This is when we started asking passing tourists to take the picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55426,"text":"You know, it's remarkable how universal"},{"time":58743,"text":"the gesture is of handing your camera to a total stranger."},{"time":61859,"text":"No one's ever refused, and luckily no one's ever run off with our camera."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66761,"text":"Back then, we had no idea how much this trip would change our lives."},{"time":70425,"text":"It's really become sacred to us."},{"time":72426,"text":"This one was taken just weeks after 9/11,"},{"time":75057,"text":"and I found myself trying to explain what had happened that day"},{"time":79272,"text":"in ways a five-year-old could understand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82032,"text":"So these photos are far more than proxies"},{"time":84639,"text":"for a single moment, or even a specific trip."},{"time":87780,"text":"They're also ways for us to freeze time"},{"time":90943,"text":"for one week in October"},{"time":94859,"text":"and reflect on our times"},{"time":97207,"text":"and how we change from year to year,"},{"time":99359,"text":"and not just physically, but in every way."},{"time":102480,"text":"Because while we take the same photo,"},{"time":104847,"text":"our perspectives change,"},{"time":107055,"text":"and she reaches new milestones,"},{"time":110408,"text":"and I get to see life through her eyes,"},{"time":112887,"text":"and how she interacts with and sees everything."},{"time":117612,"text":"This very focused time we get to spend together"},{"time":120375,"text":"is something we cherish and anticipate the entire year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125862,"text":"Recently, on one trip, we were walking,"},{"time":128923,"text":"and she stops dead in her tracks,"},{"time":131095,"text":"and she points to a red awning of the doll store"},{"time":134566,"text":"that she loved when she was little"},{"time":136990,"text":"on our earlier trips."},{"time":139262,"text":"And she describes to me the feeling she felt"},{"time":141894,"text":"as a five-year-old standing in that exact spot."},{"time":145278,"text":"She said she remembers her heart bursting out of her chest"},{"time":148307,"text":"when she saw that place for the very first time"},{"time":150968,"text":"nine years earlier."},{"time":153640,"text":"And now what she's looking at in New York"},{"time":155768,"text":"are colleges,"},{"time":157692,"text":"because she's determined to go to school in New York."},{"time":160992,"text":"And it hit me: One of the most important things"},{"time":163873,"text":"we all make are memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167882,"text":"So I want to share the idea of taking an active role"},{"time":171106,"text":"in consciously creating memories."},{"time":175039,"text":"I don't know about you, but aside from these 15 shots,"},{"time":177818,"text":"I'm not in many of the family photos."},{"time":179472,"text":"I'm always the one taking the picture."},{"time":181971,"text":"So I want to encourage everyone today"},{"time":184426,"text":"to get in the shot,"},{"time":186525,"text":"and don't hesitate to go up to someone and ask,"},{"time":189304,"text":"\"Will you take our picture?\""},{"time":191346,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}